------------
Aim_Chambers
------------

This is a medium size 10 vs 10 aim style map.

The map was a request from Tom for Live On 3 Cups.

It was based upon a HL2 prison but I chose a specific area of a prison and decided 
to use the canteen as the main location for the action in this map. 

I hope you all enjoy it,
